title: Baebody Eye Gel for Appearance of Dark Circles, Puffiness, Wrinkles and Bags. - for Under and Around Eyes - 1.7 fl oz.

Please review all ingredients for possible skin sensitivity/ allergies before use of the product.When using your airless pump dispenser for the first time, you may need to "prime" your dispenser. To prime your dispenser, pump dispenser slowly about 5 to 10 times. This process of priming will activate the vacuum pump system.
